name: Saturn Oil & Gas Inc. common share purchase warrants
longDescription: Saturn Oil & Gas Inc is a resource company engaged in the business of acquiring, exploration, and development of petroleum and natural gas resource deposits in Canada. Its focus is to advance the exploration of its oil and gas properties in west-central and Southeast Saskatchewan.
